---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
 title="Terms of Use | uplb.tools"
 description="Terms for using UPLB Tools and its volunteer projects."
>
 <Header />
 <main id="main-content" class="legal-main">
 <div class="container legal-container">
 <a href="/" class="legal-back">&larr; Home</a>

 <header class="legal-hero">
 <p class="legal-eyebrow">Legal</p>
 <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
 <p class="legal-lede">
 Last updated: July 4, 2026. By using uplb.tools or our linked volunteer projects you
 agree to these terms.
 </p>
 </header>

 <article class="legal-body">
 <section>
 <h2>Who we are</h2>
 <p>
 uplb.tools is an independent, student-led open-source collective building utilities
 for the UPLB community. We are <strong>not</strong> an official UPLB website, office,
 or administrative body. Our tools are volunteer-maintained and provided free of charge.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Scope</h2>
 <p>
 These terms apply to this hub site and generally to projects we host (Room TBA, Elbi
 GradeSim, and others under the uplbtools GitHub organization). Individual apps may
 publish supplemental terms on their own domains.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>No official status</h2>
 <p>
 Do not treat our maps, schedules, simulations, or copy as authoritative university
 records. Verify enlistment, grades, room assignments, and policy decisions with
 official UPLB systems and offices.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
 <ul>
 <li>Use tools lawfully and respectfully.</li>
 <li>Do not attempt to disrupt services, scrape aggressively, or probe for vulnerabilities.</li>
 <li>Do not misrepresent volunteer tools as official UPLB products.</li>
 <li>Contributor accounts must not be shared; edits should reflect good-faith improvements.</li>
 <li>Follow our <a href="https://github.com/uplbtools/.github/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Code of Conduct</a> in community spaces.</li>
 </ul>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Open source</h2>
 <p>
 Most project source code is published on GitHub under open-source licenses noted in
 each repository. Licenses govern code reuse; they do not grant rights to university
 trademarks or third-party data.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Contributions</h2>
 <p>
 By submitting issues, pull requests, or in-app edit proposals you grant maintainers
 the rights needed to review, merge, and deploy your contribution under the project's
 license. You represent that you have the right to submit the material.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
 <p>
 Tools are provided "as is" without warranties. Volunteers are not liable for academic,
 administrative, or personal decisions you make using our software, including incorrect
 schedules, maps, or grade simulations.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Availability</h2>
 <p>
 We may modify, suspend, or discontinue features without notice. Volunteer bandwidth
 limits how quickly bugs are fixed.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Changes</h2>
 <p>
 We may update these terms. Continued use after the "Last updated" date changes
 constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Contact</h2>
 <p>
 Questions? Use
 <a href="https://github.com/uplbtools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
 or
 <a href="https://discord.uplbtools.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Discord</a>.
 </p>
 </section>
 </article>
 </div>
 </main>
 <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
.legal-main {
 min-height: 100vh;
 padding-top: 5rem;
 padding-bottom: 2rem;
 border-bottom: 1px solid var(, border-zinc);
 }

.legal-container {
 max-width: 44rem;
 }

.legal-back {
 font-size: 0.85rem;
 color: var(, text-zinc-500);
 text-decoration: none;
 display: inline-block;
 margin-bottom: 2rem;
 }

.legal-back:hover {
 color: var(, text-zinc-200);
 }

.legal-eyebrow {
 font-size: 0.75rem;
 font-weight: 600;
 text-transform: uppercase;
 letter-spacing: 0.08em;
 color: var(, text-zinc-500);
 margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
 }

.legal-hero h1 {
 font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
 margin: 0 0 1rem;
 }

.legal-lede {
 margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
 font-size: 0.95rem;
 }

.legal-body section {
 margin-bottom: 2rem;
 }

.legal-body h2 {
 font-size: 1.15rem;
 margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
 }

.legal-body ul {
 margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
 padding-left: 1.25rem;
 }

.legal-body li {
 margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
 }

.legal-body a {
 color: var(, text-zinc-200);
 text-decoration: underline;
 text-underline-offset: 2px;
 }

.legal-body a:hover {
 color: var(, text-zinc-50);
 }
</style>
